  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b8663018083e44059281731f5b6e58c0, type: 3}
  m_Name: Line_Mona_02
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Bonbibi.DialogueLine
  speaker: 2
  isNarration: 0
  text: I come home. That's the point. The deep jungle belongs to Dokkhin Rai. His
    territory, his rules. Bonbibi and Dokkhin Rai made that agreement long before
    either of us was born, and it has kept this forest alive. The moment we stop
    respecting it is the moment the whole thing starts to come apart.
